  "detailed_description": "When a life dies, his soul goes through the Death River. Ferryman will take souls to their homeland.Ferryman likes collecting powerful souls. He offers to bring the soul back to life as a half-evil, if the soul trade him with a half of his soul.<br>There are 6 Evil Lords in the hell and they have been observing powerful souls in living world. Evil Lords kill whoever they like to recruit and lead their souls to the hell.<br>However, some talent people, hero or villian, got killed by Evil Lords. They choose to turn to half-evil and revenge to Evil Lords.<br><br>· Top-down view rpg game with roguelike features. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/c3030014d731235bfe5bcc3291fc35c6.poster.avif?t=1631888991\" width=638 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/c3030014d731235bfe5bcc3291fc35c6.webm?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/c3030014d731235bfe5bcc3291fc35c6.mp4?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>· Start with 1 selected hero, and build your team of 5 during the journey. It's to you who you want to hire.<br>· Half-demon heroes could be your teammates, as well as enemies. Learn to fight together as a efficient team, and also learn to fight against them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/340cc37ec55a869dd3347cfd171528e9.poster.avif?t=1631888991\" width=650 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/340cc37ec55a869dd3347cfd171528e9.webm?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/340cc37ec55a869dd3347cfd171528e9.mp4?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>· Over 50 random equipments and more than 10 unique equipment sets. Collect a set of equipment to activate special and powerful abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/804ca25d59b5559bd8fd83d9c5e50922.poster.avif?t=1631888991\" width=496 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/804ca25d59b5559bd8fd83d9c5e50922.webm?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/804ca25d59b5559bd8fd83d9c5e50922.mp4?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>· Challenge the Evil Lord boss at the end of the level. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/3a4a59490c037da3ec7194d893a49696.poster.avif?t=1631888991\" width=506 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/3a4a59490c037da3ec7194d893a49696.webm?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730090/extras/3a4a59490c037da3ec7194d893a49696.mp4?t=1631888991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>· You can expect more and more monsters, enemies and bosses in the future update.",
